import React from 'react'
import './App.css'
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Routes,
  Route,
  Navigate,
} from 'react-router-dom'
import LoginPage from './containers/login_page/LoginPage'
import Main from './containers/main_page/main'
// import Podcasts from './containers/podcasts/podcasts/podcasts'
import Podcasts from './newPodcasts/podcasts'
import News from './containers/news/news'
import Transfers from './containers/transfers/transfers'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import './utils/axios'

const code = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search).get('code')
console.log('code' + code)

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<Navigate to="/main" />} />
        <Route path="/login" element={<LoginPage />} />
        <Route path="/main" element={<Main />} />
        <Route path="/news" element={<News />} />
        <Route path="/transfers" element={<Transfers />} />
        <Route path="/podcasts" element={<Podcasts />} />
      </Routes>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
